article.description: — Rienk Mast posted 17 points as Bradley topped Valparaiso 71-56 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Mast scores 17 to lift Bradley past Valparaiso 71-56
article.linkText: Mast scores 17 to lift Bradley past Valparaiso 71-56
article.story: VALPARAISO, Ind. -- — Rienk Mast posted 17 points as Bradley topped Valparaiso 71-56 on Wednesday night. Terry Roberts had 13 points, six rebounds and six assists for Bradley (11-10, 5-4 Missouri Valley Conference). Malevy Leons added 12 points. Ben Krikke had 18 points and five assists for Valpo (10-11, 3-6). Kobe King added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
